                    <div class="col-md-6">
                          <h6 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600">Notice</h6>
                            <p style="font-size:12px;">A shipment offer is a shipping waiting for a travel.That means that these are your shipments offer that you created so that it can be added by a traveler on his travel</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <div class="row g-2 mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4">

                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <select id="searchInputOffers" class="form-select" oninput="liveSearchOffers(this.value)">
                                        <option value="all">ALL</option>
                                        <option value="pending">PENDING</option>
                                        <option value="accepted">ACCEPTED</option>
                                        <option value="rejected">CANCEL</option>
